### =========================================
### DYNAMIC SYSTEM PROMPTS (Runtime)
### Pass system_prompt in request body
### =========================================

### Dynamic Emotional - Sad/Melancholic
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/audio/speech
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "higgs-audio-v2",
  "input": "I never thought it would end this way. After all these years, all we've been through together.",
  "voice": "en_man",
  "response_format": "wav",
  "system_prompt": "Generate audio following instruction.\n\n<|scene_desc_start|>\nA deeply sad and melancholic delivery. The speaker is reflecting on loss with a heavy heart. Voice should crack slightly with emotion, slow pace, long pauses between phrases.\n<|scene_desc_end|>"
}

>> /Users/biz/Desktop/higgs-audio-tests/vllm2/dynamic-sad.wav

